judges: Before Bell, C. J., Musmanno, Jones, Cohen, Eagen, O’Brien and Roberts, JJ.
parties: Iron City Sand and Gravel Company, Appellant, v. Zoning Board of Adjustment.

opinions.text:
Opinion bx
Mr. Justice Cohen,
This appeal was taken to this Court after our Rule 68 1/2 became effective. However, the appellant did not comply with the requirements of Rule 68 1/2, hence this appeal must be quashed.
Appeal quashed.
opinions.author: Mr. Justice Cohen,

attorneys: Robert L. Orr, with him Reed, Orr & Reed, for appellant.
